        "text": "<h2>FAQs: Police Sirens </h2><h3>Q1: Are your police sirens suitable for volunteer responders or security vehicles?</h3><p>Yes! We carry sirens designed for both professional and volunteer use, including options for security patrols and unmarked units.</p><h3>Q2: Do your sirens include installation hardware?</h3><p>Most sirens come with mounting brackets and wiring diagrams. Check each product page for specific inclusions.</p><h3>Q3: Can I control lights and sirens from the same unit?</h3><p>Absolutely. We offer multi-function controllers that operate both lighting and siren tones in one compact package.</p><h3>Q4: Are your police sirens compliant with federal regulations?</h3><p>Yes. Our sirens meet SAE and other relevant standards for emergency vehicle warning devices.</p><h3>Q5: Do you offer installation support?</h3><p>Yes. Our team can assist with product recommendations and provide wiring documentation for your specific vehicle setup.</p>",
